{
  "name": "SmartWatch_F407",
  "description": "基于 STM32F407VET6 的智能手表嵌入式项目，采用 Bootloader+App 双工程架构，集成 FreeRTOS 实时调度、OLED UI 交互、MPU6050 姿态解算、计步器、恐龙游戏及 OTA 固件升级功能，支持 ESP8266 WiFi 通信。",
  "languages": [
    "assembly",
    "c",
    "markdown"
  ],
  "frameworks": [
    "FreeRTOS",
    "STM32 StdPeriph"
